# LIVE WEBSITE = ONE DEPLOY PATH

**Staff use http://178.128.161.215/** — existing DigitalOcean droplet. No App Platform.

## Definition of done

1. Edit code in this repo
2. **Commit** changes
3. Run **`bash ~/impect-football-dashboard/deploy-live.sh`** (pushes GitHub + syncs droplet)
   - Or user double-clicks **`Deploy to Website.command`**
4. Verify at http://178.128.161.215/ (hard refresh)

**Never** mark complete after only local changes.
**Never** rsync without also pushing to GitHub — that caused rollbacks.

## Do not

- Set up App Platform or new paid services
- Use DigitalOcean Console `update-live.sh` unless Mac deploy is broken
- Invent a second deploy path

See `deploy/HOW-WE-DEPLOY.md`.
